trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase" />-derived objects in a control that acts as a wizard.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de objetos derivados de <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase" /> em um controle que atua como um assistente.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection> class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase>-derived objects in a control that acts as a wizard, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection> classe é usada para armazenar e gerenciar uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase>-derivado objetos em um controle que atua como um assistente, como o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> controle ou <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> controle.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection> class for its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.WizardSteps%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> controlar usa o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection> de classe para seu <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.WizardSteps%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: There are multiple ways you can access the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase>-derived objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection>:
trans-unit.target: Há várias maneiras que você pode acessar o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase>-derivado objetos o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection>:

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection.Item%2A> property to directly access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase>-derived object at a specific zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection.Item%2A> propriedade para acessar diretamente um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase>-derivados do objeto em um índice com base em zero específico.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection.GetEnumerator%2A> method to create an enumerator that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection.GetEnumerator%2A> método para criar um enumerador que pode ser usado para iterar pela coleção.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection.CopyTo%2A> method to copy the contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection> collection into an <xref:System.Array> object.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection.CopyTo%2A> método para copiar o conteúdo do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection> coleção em uma <xref:System.Array> objeto.

trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection.CopyTo%2A> método para copiar o conteúdo da coleção para a matriz de base zero especificada.

trans-unit.source: Items are copied starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Itens são copiados iniciando no índice especificado da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: After the items are in an array, you can use array syntax to access the items in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection> collection.
